data.description: OPEN HOUSE 12/03/2023 from 1:00 PM to 4:00 PM! Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful 5-bedroom, 3 full bath gem is the perfect oasis for you and your loved ones. You'll be captivated by the stunning laminate wood flooring, creating an elegant and modern ambiance. The luxurious huge master suite has its own private master bath featuring a separate garden tub and shower, double vanity, and an enormous walk-in closet. Whip up gourmet meals and entertain guests in the spacious kitchen. Step outside onto the covered patio and indulge in the enchanting atmosphere. This space is perfect for creating beautiful memories. Location, location, location! This home is conveniently located near Randolph AFB and Fort Sam, making commuting a breeze. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this stunning home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the true meaning of luxurious living. Your dream home awaits!
